    "title": "Mwana wa Mtu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mwana wa mtu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>&quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; ilikuwa njia aliyopendelea Yesu kujirejelea. Kifungu hiki ni cha kipekee katika Kigiriki na Kiingereza. Kinatafsiri kifungu cha Kiebrania ben <em>’adam</em>, ambacho kinamaanisha &quot;binadamu&quot; au &quot;mtu&quot; (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:1-Ezek2:8\">Ezekieli 2:1–8</a>). Yesu alipenda jina hili kwa sababu halikusababisha mijadala kama vyeo &quot;Kristo&quot; au &quot;Masihi.&quot;</p><p>Injili zinatumia msemo huo kwa njia tatu:</p><ol><li><p>Asili ya matumizi ya Yesu ya jina hilo inatoka kwa <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">Danieli 7:13–14</a>. Katika kifungu hiki, mtu wa kimasihi &quot;kama Mwana wa Mtu&quot; (ikimaanisha &quot;kama mwanadamu&quot;) anafika na mawingu ya mbinguni na kupokea utukufu na nguvu kuu. Yesu alijiona kama yule ambaye angerudi duniani katika mawingu ya mbinguni (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">Marko 8:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:26\">13:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">14:62</a>). Wakati mwingine, Yesu alitumia &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kuelezea jukumu lake kama hakimu, mkombozi, mwokozi, na yule anayerekebisha makosa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:23\">Mathayo 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:41\">13:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28\">19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:27\">24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:37\">37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:44\">44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">25:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:64\">26:64</a>).</p></li><li><p>Yesu mara nyingi alijiita &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; ili kuonyesha kuwa alikuwa mkombozi anayeteseka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:40\">Mathayo 12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:9\">17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:12\">12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:22\">22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:18\">20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:2\">26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:45\">45</a>). Wazo hili linatokana na <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">Isaya 52:13–53:12</a>.</p></li><li><p>Wakati mwingine, Yesu alitumia &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kujieleza kama mwakilishi wa wanadamu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:20\">Mathayo 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:19\">11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:8\">12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:32\">32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:37\">13:37</a>). Kitabu cha Ezekieli kinatumia &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kwa njia sawa (tazama tena, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:1-Ezek2:8\">Ezekieli 2:1–8</a>).</p></li></ol><p>Yesu hakutumia &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kutenganisha ubinadamu wake na uungu wake kama &quot;Mwana wa Mungu&quot; inavyofanya wakati mwingine. Kwa kutumia jina hili, Yesu alijitambulisha kama Masihi au Kristo (mteule wa Mungu) kwa masharti yake mwenyewe. Alitumia &quot;Mwana wa Mtu&quot; kuelezea utambulisho wake kamili na alidokeza kwamba wale waliomtazama na kumsikiliza wanapaswa kutambua yeye ni nani.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:1-Ezek2:8\">Ezekieli 2:1–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:1\">3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:4\">4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:10\">10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:17\">17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:25\">25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:1\">4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">Danieli 7:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:17\">8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:18-Matt8:22\">Mathayo 8:18–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6\">9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:23\">10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:19\">11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:8\">12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:32\">32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:40\">40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:37\">13:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:41\">41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:13\">16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27-Matt16:28\">27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:9\">17:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:12\">12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:22\">22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28\">19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:18\">20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:27\">24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:37-Matt24:39\">37–39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:44\">44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">25:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:2\">26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:45\">45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:64\">64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:10\">Marko 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:51\">Yohana 1:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:13-John3:14\">3:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:27\">5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:27\">6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:53\">53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:62\">62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28\">8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:35\">9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23\">12:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:34\">34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31\">13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:56\">Matendo 7:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:6\">Waebrania 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:13\">Ufunuo 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:14\">14:14</a></p>",
